author: Screen Junkies
description:
Run from it, hide from it, but the Honest Trailer for Final Destination will get you in the end. Enjoy this buffet of wacky physics and death that made you fear plane rides, aggressively slipping in the shower, silent killer ninja buses, and mild gusts of wind that signify your doom!

Comment below with the dumbest movie death you've ever seen!
